Application Installation (AppInstall) is used to install a Windows\'ae\loch\f0  CE\hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 based application onto a Windows \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 CE\hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 based device}{\insrsid1854247 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
 such as a Pocket PC device}{\insrsid12476003 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 . This paper discusses AppInstall and is specifically targeted to creating a setup program that supports multiple devices}{\insrsid6643857 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 . 
