Application Installation (AppInstall) is the mechanism used to install Windows CE\hich\f0 \endash \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 based applications onto a Windows CE\hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 
based device. AppInstall supports multiple installation methods, such as desktop-to-device, web-to-device, storage card-to-device, and device-to-device.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 AppInstall is comprised of three components:
