 .cab file, which is the file format for distributing multiple files. CabWiz is used by the application developer and is part of the }{\insrsid1854247 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Pocket PC}{\insrsid12476003 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
 software development kit (SDK).
