\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Application Manager (CeAppMgr) is the desktop Microsoft\'ae\loch\f0  ActiveSync component that provides a desktop-to-device application management tool. It is responsible for adding and removing applications on the }{
\insrsid6643857 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Pocket PC}{\insrsid12476003 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  device and deleting the applicat\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 
ion files from the desktop computer. Application Manager is used by both the application developer and the end user and is included with every installation of ActiveSync.
