\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 WCELoad is the }{\insrsid6643857 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Pocket PC}{\insrsid12476003 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  tool that unpacks a }{\insrsid6643857 \hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 Pocket PC}{\insrsid12476003 
\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0  .cab file to install an a\hich\af0\dbch\af13\loch\f0 pplication on a device. WCELoad is used by the end user and is included with most Windows CE\hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 based devices.
